---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: Products
permalink: /products/
eyebrow:
  en: Our Products
  vi: Sản phẩm
  zh: 产品
heading:
  en: Nutrition Designed for Every Stage.
  vi: Giải pháp dinh dưỡng cho mọi giai đoạn.
  zh: 为每个阶段设计的营养方案。
lead:
  en: Real Nam Viet feed lines — pig, poultry, duck, cattle, goat, quail, fish and frog — built on scientific nutrition and branded packaging.
  vi: Dòng thức ăn Nam Việt thực tế — heo, gia cầm, vịt, bò, dê, chim cút, cá và ếch — dựa trên dinh dưỡng khoa học và bao bì thương hiệu.
  zh: 南越真实饲料产品线——猪、禽、鸭、牛、羊、鹌鹑、鱼与蛙——基于科学营养与品牌包装。
---

<div class="products-stats reveal">
  <div>
    <strong>{{ about.distribution.commercial.value }}</strong>
    <span class="lang en">{{ about.distribution.commercial.en }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ about.distribution.commercial.vi }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ about.distribution.commercial.zh }}</span>
  </div>
  <div>
    <strong>{{ about.distribution.internal.value }}</strong>
    <span class="lang en">{{ about.distribution.internal.en }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ about.distribution.internal.vi }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ about.distribution.internal.zh }}</span>
  </div>
  <div>
    <strong>{{ about.distribution.dealers.value }}</strong>
    <span class="lang en">{{ about.distribution.dealers.en }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ about.distribution.dealers.vi }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ about.distribution.dealers.zh }}</span>
  </div>
  <div>
    <strong>{{ about.capacity.poultryLine.value }}</strong>
    <span class="lang en">t / year feed capacity</span>
    <span class="lang vi">tấn / năm công suất TACN</span>
    <span class="lang zh">吨 / 年饲料产能</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="products__grid products__grid--page">
  {% for product in collections.products %}
  <a href="{{ product.url | url }}" class="pcard pcard--media" style="--pc:{{ product.data.color }}">
    {% if product.data.image %}
    <span class="pcard__media"><img src="{{ product.data.image | url }}" alt="{{ product.data.code }}" loading="lazy" width="400" height="560" decoding="async"></span>
    {% endif %}
    <span class="pcard__code">{{ product.data.code }}</span>
    <span class="pcard__name">
      <span class="lang en">{{ product.data.title.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ product.data.title.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ product.data.title.zh }}</span>
    </span>
    <span class="pcard__more">
      <span class="lang en">Learn more</span>
      <span class="lang vi">Xem thêm</span>
      <span class="lang zh">了解更多</span> →
    </span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<p class="page-actions">
  <a class="btn btn--solid" href="{{ '/downloads/' | url }}">
    <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.downloadCatalog }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.downloadCatalog }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.downloadCatalog }}</span>
  </a>
</p>
